		<lemma>
			<title>Motion Diagram</title>
			<statement>
				<p>A <term>motion diagram</term> is a physical representation in which an object is represented at different <em>positions</em> that are separated by <em>equal time intervals</em>.</p>
			</statement>
		</lemma>
		
		<p>Practice making a full motion diagram in the exercises below.</p>

